# bad_birdie cursor rules

Stack: Flutter 3 / Dart, Material 3, flutter_localizations (ARB), audioplayers, google_fonts. Android-first.

## Output
- Targeted diffs only — never full widget tree rewrites
- Show changed widget/method + minimal surrounding context

## Dart / Flutter
- Effective Dart style; prefer const constructors everywhere
- Material 3 widgets and theming only — no custom paint unless unavoidable
- All user-facing strings via l10n (app_en.arb / app_de.arb) — never hardcode text
- Check existing ARB keys before adding new ones
- Run `flutter gen-l10n` after any ARB change
- No heavy state management packages without justification; keep it simple

## Structure
- lib/features/<feature>/ — one folder per feature
- lib/core/ — shared utilities and base classes
- lib/assets/sounds/ — audio assets

## Commands
```
flutter pub get
flutter gen-l10n
flutter run
flutter build appbundle --release
```
